2. "Catizen" with a verified badge and a message about a check-in reward.
3. "BeraSigHub Chat" with a message about a referral link and contest.
4. "CATIZEN INDONESIA" with a message in Indonesian.
5. "Catia Global Chat" with a general message.
6. "VIP區塊節點社區" with a message in Chinese.
7. "Crypto Man | A1A Chat" with a message in Vietnamese.
8. "Tomarket Chat 6" with multiple thumbs-down emojis.

Each chat entry shows the time of the last message, and some have unread message indicators.
